<plot>Guy suffers silently through life's daily assaults: the endless droning of the ceiling fan, the constant flicker of the computer monitor, the nagging abuses of the secretary and the incessant ranting of his boss. But all this changes one day when the appearance of a stranger disrupts the monotony and causes him to question his very existence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?225473</url></doc>
